metadata.name: threads of being
metadata.description:
A still of generative art created by ChatGPT via prompts for p5.js code and stitching by totty.eth. This is a version of their fourth collaboration with heavy smearing on top of its usual output. This piece invites the viewer to look closely at the color and texture hidden between the lines. The underlying image is a collage of clouds, trees, horizontal lines, and noise, as interpreted by the chatbot.

To learn more about this collection and how to mint these pieces, please see the following link: [https://mirror.xyz/totty.eth/EeSOBtP1OMT__YAh4lHxeLXjsR53wCFbQFWmWYojb_8](https://mirror.xyz/totty.eth/EeSOBtP1OMT__YAh4lHxeLXjsR53wCFbQFWmWYojb_8)
